    QP->>Caikit: Forward to transformer-container<br/>HTTP/8080, plaintext (pod-local)
    Caikit->>TGIS: Inference request<br/>gRPC/8033, plaintext (pod-local)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated text response
    Caikit-->>QP: HTTP response
    QP-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC call<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443, TLS 1.2+ (SIMPLE)
    Gateway->>QP: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8012, mTLS (Istio)
    QP->>Caikit: Forward to transformer-container<br/>gRPC/8085 (h2c), plaintext (pod-local)
    Caikit->>TGIS: Inference request<br/>gRPC/8033, plaintext (pod-local)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated text response
    Caikit-->>QP: gRPC response
    QP-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
